{"tid":986572,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"學唔到混聲 好灰","createTime":"2019-01-18T14:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T06:33:12.000Z","uid":115504,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"80305b7aa7aa85888121376d8c1f86210d8cfb73","tid":986572,"uid":115504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"我係好細個就已經接觸唱歌<br />\n但係變左聲之後覺得自己把聲好難聽<br />\n好薄<br />\n身邊嘅朋友都已經成功開發混聲<br />\n我比佢哋更早研究<br />\n更多練習 嘗試<br />\n但係佢哋有人岩岩先開始唱歌<br />\n岩岩先開始自學混聲 即刻就得<br />\n仲要唱得好好聽<br />\n我唔係要求自己叻過佢地<br />\n我只係覺得自己咁努力<br />\n不及人地一半<br />\n我唱嘅混聲都係聽落去好假 好嘈<br />\n類似皮囊嘅「燒」<br />\n但係無佢咁真<br />\n有無巴打都係咁？<br />\n想知自己究竟咩問題"},{"pid":"4957fb4ba7ef54aef21c5767b566febf46e957c6","tid":986572,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:59:25.000Z","msg":"之前跟網上既片用彈唇學混聲<br />\n唔知學得啱唔啱<br />\n但係高音確實輕鬆咗<br />\n唔再係用喉嚨扯上去"},{"pid":"a4cb5d2dd59008bfb7bf2231e1ec4dc7735ece96","tid":986572,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4957fb4ba7ef54aef21c5767b566febf46e957c6","tid":986572,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:59:25.000Z","msg":"之前跟網上既片用彈唇學混聲<br />\n唔知學得啱唔啱<br />\n但係高音確實輕鬆咗<br />\n唔再係用喉嚨扯上去"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"彈唇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fd37f56ca341afbc4b58724809dc76d545c1a6","tid":986572,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:10:58.000Z","msg":"起碼至少2年先得喎，只能講你d朋友勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798d8cc063eb09ebd66c3a7b578c15cd9e3fd8e9","tid":986572,"uid":158145,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a4cb5d2dd59008bfb7bf2231e1ec4dc7735ece96","tid":986572,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4957fb4ba7ef54aef21c5767b566febf46e